 still blows my mind how many people think that I am Mark. It's happened plenty before. See for yourself...https://youtu.be/Imto3sO88Mc. and the story that goes with it...
https://www.ocregister.com/2019/07/20/mark-hamill-lookalike-fluke-skywalker-blows-minds-at-comic-con-as-star-wars-fans-press-in-for-photos/amp/

EDIT - Most Viral? Heck yeah! Thank you my dudes. 
On another note, I can't thank you all enough for being so kind to me and saying such nice things. The Imgur community is the most kind and generous community out of all of the social media that I am on. From my first visit to the Ronald McDonald House in 2017 at Christmas time to the toy drive I did on Giving Tuesday last November, you guys have been with me all the way and have been totally supportive. I can't tell you how much it means to me that you are helping so many little kids who are really experiencing one of the worst times in their life. Your generosity gets them a new Star Wars toy and they forget about the pain for a while. You all turn tears into laughter. Kids that were in the room only a few minutes before upset, sick and scared become a whole different person when they get a lightsaber in their hands or a Grogu to keep.(Kids love beating the hell out of each other with lightsabers. LOL) Remember how much it meant to you when you were little kid and someone was very kind to you and surprised you with a new toy? That's how they feel. I can't do this level of giving without all of you. I can't thank you enough and I genuinely love you guys for your generosity and the fact you care about other human beings that you don't know and will never meet. You all deserve all of the credit in my opinion. My job is just to buy the toys and take them there and interact with the kids whenever possible. I truly don't think of myself as anything more than a Dad from Cincinnati, who volunteers to help out charities. Thanks again and may the force be with you!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/D0AXgCI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[imflukeskywalker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well said.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bLd101P</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/506fXwL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TTK3dx6.jpg" style="max-